Sexy phone conversations between a man and woman provide the basis of this unique Dutch drama. It is based upon a 1994 "interactive" play wherein the audience, ensconced in individual cubicles containing video monitors, was able to participate by switching back and forth between the characters. The "06" is equivalent to the U.S. premium 900-telephone numbers which are often used as sex-talk, "chat" lines. The story switches between two callers. The woman is at home and frequently spends the time answering the man's questions. He calls from his office. They call each other once a week, and the story covers 11 of their calls. On the phone, they share their sexual fantasies and white lies while masturbating (This is implied, not explicitly done). ~ Sandra Brennan, Allrovi
